    "chapter": "Agriculture & Green Revolution",
    "chapterIndex": 18,
    "qNoInChapter": 4,
    "question": "Assertion (A) : The dry zone of India has a predominantly agrarian economy. Reason (R) : It has large potential for the second Green Revolution. Select the correct answer from the code given below: Code :",
